---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Get Involved"
  description="Local Wabash businesses and nonprofits: share how you're using AI, express your interest, and join the community conversation."
>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="text-amber-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Community Participation</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-4">
      Get Involved
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
      wabash.ai is a community resource, not a one-way broadcast.
      Local businesses and nonprofits are what make it useful. Here's how to take part.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Ways to participate -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-1 gap-6">

      <!-- Share your story -->
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-3xl">&#128172;</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Share how you're using AI</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you're a Wabash-area business or nonprofit that's started experimenting with AI tools —
              even just a little — we'd like to hear about it. What did you try? What worked?
              What didn't? Your experience is more useful to other local organizations than anything
              an outsider can write.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Stories (shared with your permission) help the community see what's realistic and
              practical, rather than the hype-cycle version of AI that dominates the national media.
            </p>
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@wabash.ai?subject=My%20AI%20Story&body=Hi%2C%0A%0AHere%27s%20how%20we%27ve%20been%20experimenting%20with%20AI%20at%20%5Byour%20organization%5D%3A%0A%0A%5Bwrite%20here%5D%0A%0AOK%20to%20share%20this%20publicly%3A%20%5Byes%20%2F%20no%20%2F%20anonymously%20OK%5D"
              class="inline-block bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-500 text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
            >
              Share your story
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Express interest in learning -->
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-3xl">&#128202;</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Tell us what you need to learn</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              What questions do you have about AI that haven't been answered yet?
              What would you need to understand before you'd feel comfortable trying AI tools
              in your work? Knowing what's holding people back helps shape the learning
              resources and class topics on this site.
            </p>
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@wabash.ai?subject=AI%20Question%20or%20Learning%20Need&body=Hi%2C%0A%0AHere%27s%20what%20I%20need%20to%20understand%20better%3A%0A%0A%5Bwrite%20here%5D%0A%0AOrganization%20type%20(optional)%3A%20%5Bsmall%20business%20%2F%20nonprofit%20%2F%20other%5D"
              class="inline-block border border-amber-600 text-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-50 font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
            >
              Tell us what you need
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Suggest a resource -->
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-3xl">&#128218;</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Suggest a learning resource</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Found something genuinely useful — a free course, a clear article, a practical tool?
              The <a href="/learn" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-medium">Learn page</a>
              grows through community input. Send a link and a sentence about why it was useful to you.
            </p>
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@wabash.ai?subject=Resource%20Suggestion&body=Hi%2C%0A%0AHere%27s%20a%20resource%20I%20found%20useful%3A%0A%0AURL%3A%20%5Blink%5D%0AWhy%20it%27s%20useful%3A%20%5Bwrite%20here%5D"
              class="inline-block border border-gray-300 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
            >
              Suggest a resource
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who this is for -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-6 py-6 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Who this is for</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
      wabash.ai is aimed at Wabash-area small businesses and nonprofits — the corner restaurant,
      the three-person law office, the food pantry, the historical society, the family farm.
      Organizations where one or two people wear all the hats and don't have a technology
      department to figure this out for them.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      If that's you, this is for you.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact direct -->
  <section class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-8">
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
      General questions or comments:
      <a href="mailto:hello@wabash.ai" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700 font-medium">hello@wabash.ai</a>
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
